caption.text: It’s SO easy to get stuck in consumption. Fooling yourself into thinking you’re ‘learning’. One thing I learned the hard way is that learning only takes place when you’re in the game. You learn something, then immediately apply it. Otherwise it goes in one ear and out the other. #socialmedia #socialmediamarketing #instagramgrowth #contentcreatoradvice

caption.text: One of the harshest truths on social media. Sure, you can make it regardless. But putting effort into how you look makes it a whole lot easier. And I’ve found in my own content that when I have a nicer haircut, get my beard trimmed, wear nicer clothes or have a tan, then my videos perform better. #instagramgrowth #socialmediamarketing #philosophy
